# qt5-meego-platform-plugin

qt5-meego-platform-plugin is the Qt platform integration plugin for Nokia N9

## Dependencies

### Build dependencies

* pkg-config
* xcb
* dbus-1
* xrender
* xi
* sm
* fontconfig
* freetype6
* glib2.0

